---
layout: base.njk
title: Match Box 313 | Match Night, zéro effort
---
<div class="poster-container">
    {% image "/assets/hero_bg.jpg", "Match Box 313", "(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px", "poster-img", "eager" %}





    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="hero-badge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 7l4.76 3.46-1.82 5.54H9.06l-1.82-5.54L12 7z"></path></svg> &nbsp;Detroit-style · Soccer Night</span>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Match Night,<br><span class="highlight">zéro effort</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Tout est prêt. Tu chauffes. Tu profites.</p>
            <a href="#products" class="cta-btn">Commander ma Match Box <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z"></path></svg></a>
            <div class="scroll-hint">
                <span>Découvrir les box</span>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
</div>

<!-- Product Section — in normal flow, pulled up over the poster bottom with negative margin -->
<section id="products" class="products">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal-item">
            <h2 class="section-title">La Match Box <svg class="nav-icon" style="color:var(--primary-accent)" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 11h.01"/><path d="M11 15h.01"/><path d="M16 16h.01"/><path d="m2 16 20 6-6-20A20 20 0 0 0 2 16"/></svg></h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Choisissez votre format. Les cadeaux sont pour nous.</p>
            
            <!-- In-section Countdown -->
            <div id="countdown-ticker" class="section-countdown" style="display: none;">
                <span class="ticker-label">⏳ Fermeture des commandes pour <span id="next-match-name">...</span> dans :</span>
                <div class="ticker-clock">
                    <span id="days">00</span>j <span id="hours">00</span>h <span id="minutes">00</span>m <span id="seconds">00</span>s
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="product-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 450px)); justify-content: center;">
            {% for box in boxes %}
            <div class="product-card reveal-item">
                <div class="card-img-wrap">
                    {% image box.image, box.title, "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw", "card-img" %}
                    <span class="price-tag">{{ box.price }}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="card-info">
                    <h3>{{ box.title }}</h3>
                    <p>{{ box.description }}</p>
                    <button class="card-btn">Commander</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section id="how" class="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal-item">
            <h2 class="section-title">Comment ça marche ?</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Simple, rapide, délicieux.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-grid">
            <!-- Continuous vertical progress line (mobile only) -->
            <div class="steps-progress-v">
                <div class="steps-progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step-card reveal-item">
                <p class="step-number">01</p>
                <div class="step-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Commandez ta Box</h3>
                <p>Choisis ta box préférée et reçois-la rapidement chez toi, prête à être chauffée.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card reveal-item">
                <p class="step-number">02</p>
                <div class="step-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Chauffez sans stress</h3>
                <p>Quelques minutes au four — et ta pizza Detroit-style croustille à la perfection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card reveal-item">
                <p class="step-number">03</p>
                <div class="step-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"></path><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Savourez le match</h3>
                <p>Installe-toi, share avec tes amis et profite pleinement de chaque minute de jeu !</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Social Proof Section -->
<section id="reviews" class="reviews-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="reviews-grid">
            <!-- Global Rating Card -->
            <div class="rating-card reveal-item">
                <div class="rating-header">
                    <span class="rating-number">4.8</span>
                    <span class="rating-max">/5</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stars">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
                </div>
                <p class="rating-source">Moyenne des avis Food Truck</p>
                <div class="trust-badge">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12c0-1-.1-2-.3-2.9H12v5.5h5.7c-.2 1.3-1 2.5-2.1 3.3v2.8h3.4c2-1.8 3.1-4.5 3.1-7.7z"></path></svg> Verified Reviews
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Featured Testimonial -->
            <div class="review-main reveal-item">
                <svg class="quote-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V20c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg>
                <p class="review-text">
                    "Accueil chaleureux, agréable et souriant, rien à redire. Les pizzas sont excellentes et bien fournies. Jamais déçu, hâte d'être à la journée pizza car on se régale à chaque commande. Je recommande à 1000% !"
                </p>
                <div class="review-author">— Client Fidèle (Google Review)</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Chef's Note -->
            <div class="chef-note-card reveal-item">
                <div class="chef-avatar">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Le mot du Chef</h3>
                <p>
                    "Dans mes Match Box, la pizza Detroit n'est que le début. Tout tourne autour de la qualité : mes <strong>viandes fumées maison</strong> et mes <strong>entrées artisanales</strong> sont au cœur de l'expérience. C'est cette même exigence que vous retrouvez chaque jour à mon Food Truck."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Menu Gallery -->
<section id="menu-gallery" class="gallery-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal-item">
            <h2 class="section-title">L'Ardoise du Chef <svg class="nav-icon" style="color:var(--primary-accent)" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"></circle></svg></h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Focus sur nos pépites fumées et croustillantes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            {% for item in gallery %}
            <div class="gallery-card reveal-item {{ 'tall' if loop.index == 2 or loop.index == 5 }} {{ 'wide' if loop.index == 1 }}">
                <div class="gallery-img-container">
                    {% image item.image, item.title, "(max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw", "gallery-img" %}
                    <div class="gallery-overlay">



                        <div class="gallery-info">
                            <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
                            <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Social Hub (Find Us) -->
<section id="community" class="social-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal-item">
            <h2 class="section-title">Rejoignez la team 313 <svg class="nav-icon" style="color:var(--primary-accent)" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg></h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Suivez nos aventures et partagez vos Match Box.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="social-grid">
            <!-- Facebook -->
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/313pizza.fr/" target="_blank" class="social-card fb reveal-item">
                <div class="social-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path></svg></div>
                <div class="social-content">
                    <h3>Facebook</h3>
                    <p>Actu, évènements et photos de la communauté.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="social-arrow"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg></div>
            </a>

            <!-- Instagram -->
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/313pizza.fr/" target="_blank" class="social-card ig reveal-item">
                <div class="social-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg></div>
                <div class="social-content">
                    <h3>Instagram</h3>
                    <p>Le plein de foodporn avant le coup d'envoi.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="social-arrow"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg></div>
            </a>

            <!-- Discord (Internal Link or Placeholder) -->
            <div class="social-card discord reveal-item">
                <div class="social-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="12" r="1"></circle><circle cx="15" cy="12" r="1"></circle><path d="M7.5 7.5c3.5-1 5.5-1 9 0"></path><path d="M7 16.5c3.5 1 6.5 1 10 0"></path><path d="M15.5 17c0 1 1.5 3 2 3 1.5 0 2.833-1.667 3.5-3 .667-1.667.5-5.833-1.5-11.5-1.457-1.015-3-1.34-4.5-1.5l-1 2.5"></path><path d="M8.5 17c0 1-1.5 3-2 3-1.5 0-2.833-1.667-3.5-3-.667-1.667-.5-5.833 1.5-11.5 1.457-1.015 3-1.34 4.5-1.5l1 2.5"></path></svg></div>
                <div class="social-content">
                    <h3>Discord</h3>
                    <p>Le salon privé arrive bientôt pour le Mondial !</p>
                </div>
                <span class="social-badge">À venir</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
